}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian, who's been coaching his daughter her entire life, long ago learned how to walk the fine line between parent and coach.\", \"from\": 3684, \"to\": 3809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brian\", \"from\": 3684, \"to\": 3689}, {\"ngram\": \"his daughter\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3723}, {\"ngram\": \"the fine line\", \"from\": 3770, \"to\": 3783}, {\"ngram\": \"parent\", \"from\": 3792, \"to\": 3798}, {\"ngram\": \"coach\", \"from\": 3803, \"to\": 3808}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He knew that finding the delicate balance was especially critical at that moment.\", \"from\": 3810, \"to\": 3891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the delicate balance\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3851}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 3879, \"to\": 3890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He gave her space and time, eventually texting only to see if she might want to work out the next morning.\", \"from\": 3892, \"to\": 3998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her space\", \"from\": 3900, \"to\": 3909}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3914, \"to\": 3918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Carey said yes, he felt a glimmer of hope but knew to tread lightly.\", \"from\": 3999, \"to\": 4072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4004, \"end\": 4009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1871048703113533e-26, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a glimmer\", \"from\": 4028, \"to\": 4037}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 4041, \"to\": 4045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian arrived at the gym and promptly shooed away the national team coordinators and other assembled staff, leaving no one in the gym save father and daughter and a Japanese gymnast fine-tuning her beam routine.\", \"from\": 4074, \"to\": 4285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4239, \"end\": 4247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9999989702024168, \"rank\": 4.877844295058369e-07, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brian\", \"from\": 4074, \"to\": 4079}, {\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 4091, \"to\": 4098}, {\"ngram\": \"the national team coordinators\", \"from\": 4124, \"to\": 4154}, {\"ngram\": \"other assembled staff\", \"from\": 4159, \"to\": 4180}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 4190, \"to\": 4196}, {\"ngram\": \"the gym save father\", \"from\": 4200, \"to\": 4219}, {\"ngram\": \"daughter\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4232}, {\"ngram\": \"her beam routine\", \"from\": 4268, \"to\": 4284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jade talked through her worries and disappointments.\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jade\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4290}, {\"ngram\": \"her worries\", \"from\": 4306, \"to\": 4317}, {\"ngram\": \"disappointments\", \"from\": 4322, \"to\": 4337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian listened patiently, but when Jade paused long enough to allow him to insert a thought, he offered a suggestion.\", \"from\": 4339, \"to\": 4456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4374, \"end\": 4378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Mitchell\", \"score\": 0.9999897555605425, \"rank\": 1.007880114965091e-05, \"text\": \"Jade\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Mitchell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Mitchell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brian\", \"from\": 4339, \"to\": 4344}, {\"ngram\": \"a thought\", \"from\": 4421, \"to\": 4430}, {\"ngram\": \"a suggestion\", \"from\": 4443, \"to\": 4455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What if,\\\" Brian prodded his daughter, \\\"the worst day of your life could turn into the best day?\\\"\", \"from\": 4458, \"to\": 4555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brian\", \"from\": 4469, \"to\": 4474}, {\"ngram\": \"his daughter\", \"from\": 4483, \"to\": 4495}, {\"ngram\": \"the worst day\", \"from\": 4498, \"to\": 4511}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 4515, \"to\": 4524}, {\"ngram\": \"the best day\", \"from\": 4541, \"to\": 4553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And then I saw a spark,\\\" Brian said.\", \"from\": 4557, \"to\": 4594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a spark\", \"from\": 4573, \"to\": 4580}, {\"ngram\": \"Brian\", \"from\": 4583, \"to\": 4588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next day, Carey scored a 14.366 in the floor exercise and won Olympic gold.\", \"from\": 4595, \"to\": 4674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4609, \"end\": 4614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1871048703113533e-26, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the floor exercise\", \"from\": 4634, \"to\": 4652}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is that spark that Oregon State continues to fuel for Carey.\", \"from\": 4676, \"to\": 4739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4733, \"end\": 4738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1871048703113533e-26, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that spark\", \"from\": 4682, \"to\": 4692}, {\"ngram\": \"Oregon State\", \"from\": 4698, \"to\": 4710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement It not only takes a village to do what Carey is trying to do; it takes the very fluid desktop calendar housed on Brian's laptop.\", \"from\": 4741, \"to\": 4884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4795, \"end\": 4800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1871048703113533e-26, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a village\", \"from\": 4773, \"to\": 4782}, {\"ngram\": \"the very fluid desktop calendar\", \"from\": 4826, \"to\": 4857}, {\"ngram\": \"Brian's laptop\", \"from\": 4868, \"to\": 4882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Meet dates are in pen,\\\" said Brian, who joined the Oregon State coaching staff this year.\", \"from\": 4886, \"to\": 4976, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Meet dates\", \"from\": 4887, \"to\": 4897}, {\"ngram\": \"pen\", \"from\": 4905, \"to\": 4908}, {\"ngram\": \"Brian\", \"from\": 4916, \"to\": 4921}, {\"ngram\": \"the Oregon State coaching staff\", \"from\": 4934, \"to\": 4965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everything else is in pencil.\\\"\", \"from\": 4977, \"to\": 5008, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everything\", \"from\": 4978, \"to\": 4988}, {\"ngram\": \"pencil\", \"from\": 5000, \"to\": 5006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The goal all season has been to do the seemingly undoable - pursueNCAAexcellence, without jilting Olympic training.\", \"from\": 5010, \"to\": 5125, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The goal\", \"from\": 5010, \"to\": 5018}, {\"ngram\": \"the seemingly undoable - pursueNCAAexcellence\", \"from\": 5045, \"to\": 5090}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic training\", \"from\": 5108, \"to\": 5124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To the untrained ear, it sounds decidedly uncomplicated - do gymnastics for Oregon State, which in turn equates to prep for theOlympics.\", \"from\": 5126, \"to\": 5262, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the untrained ear\", \"from\": 5129, \"to\": 5146}, {\"ngram\": \"decidedly uncomplicated - do gymnastics\", \"from\": 5158, \"to\": 5197}, {\"ngram\": \"Oregon State\", \"from\": 5202, \"to\": 5214}, {\"ngram\": \"turn\", \"from\": 5225, \"to\": 5229}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympics\", \"from\": 5250, \"to\": 5261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not that simple.\", \"from\": 5263, \"to\": 5285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the risk of sounding crass, college gymnastics is easier.\", \"from\": 5287, \"to\": 5347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 5290, \"to\": 5298}, {\"ngram\": \"sounding crass\", \"from\": 5302, \"to\": 5316}, {\"ngram\": \"college gymnastics\", \"from\": 5318, \"to\": 5336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To score a perfect 10 (the NCAA still uses the old system of scoring) requires more precision and far less from Carey's very sizable bag of tricks.\", \"from\": 5348, \"to\": 5495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5375, \"end\": 5379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999979345375, \"rank\": 2.0653479421321528e-09, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 5460, \"end\": 5465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1871048703113533e-26, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the old system\", \"from\": 5391, \"to\": 5405}, {\"ngram\": \"scoring\", \"from\": 5409, \"to\": 5416}, {\"ngram\": \"more precision\", \"from\": 5427, \"to\": 5441}, {\"ngram\": \"tricks\", \"from\": 5488, \"to\": 5494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is equal parts unnecessary and borderline unwise to perform her harder skills during the Oregon State season, a far longer and more meet-heavy calendar than the elite season.\", \"from\": 5496, \"to\": 5673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"equal parts\", \"from\": 5502, \"to\": 5513}, {\"ngram\": \"her harder skills\", \"from\": 5559, \"to\": 5576}, {\"ngram\": \"the Oregon State season\", \"from\": 5584, \"to\": 5607}, {\"ngram\": \"the elite season\", \"from\": 5656, \"to\": 5672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That means Carey essentially has to devise separate routines for each apparatus and train both with equal gusto.\", \"from\": 5675, \"to\": 5787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5686, \"end\": 5691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1871048703113533e-26, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"separate routines\", \"from\": 5718, \"to\": 5735}, {\"ngram\": \"each apparatus\", \"from\": 5740, \"to\": 5754}, {\"ngram\": \"equal gusto\", \"from\": 5775, \"to\": 5786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most days, Carey does her collegiate sets and then concentrates on her international assignments.\", \"from\": 5788, \"to\": 5885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5799, \"end\": 5804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1871048703113533e-26, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her collegiate sets\", \"from\": 5810, \"to\": 5829}, {\"ngram\": \"her international assignments\", \"from\": 5855, \"to\": 5884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has purposefully - and reluctantly - backed off of the number of events she's competed in this season (she did 55 routines a year ago compared to 42 this year).\", \"from\": 5886, \"to\": 6050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 5941, \"to\": 5951}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 5955, \"to\": 5961}, {\"ngram\": \"this season\", \"from\": 5980, \"to\": 5991}, {\"ngram\": \"55 routines\", \"from\": 6001, \"to\": 6012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, it's a lot to juggle, and it's the reason most women take time off from their college obligations during Olympic years.\", \"from\": 6051, \"to\": 6177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 6063, \"to\": 6068}, {\"ngram\": \"the reason\", \"from\": 6089, \"to\": 6099}, {\"ngram\": \"most women\", \"from\": 6100, \"to\": 6110}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 6116, \"to\": 6120}, {\"ngram\": \"their college obligations\", \"from\": 6130, \"to\": 6155}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic years\", \"from\": 6163, \"to\": 6176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not a little girls' sport anymore; it's a women's sport,\\\" said Oregon State head coach Tanya Chaplin.\", \"from\": 6179, \"to\": 6286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6272, \"end\": 6285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanya_Chaplin\", \"score\": 0.9999986923184588, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tanya Chaplin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanya_Chaplin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanya_Chaplin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little girls' sport\", \"from\": 6189, \"to\": 6210}, {\"ngram\": \"a women's sport\", \"from\": 6225, \"to\": 6240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You do not have to put one aside for the other.\", \"from\": 6287, \"to\": 6335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's a lot.\", \"from\": 6336, \"to\": 6351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 6345, \"to\": 6350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not easy.\", \"from\": 6352, \"to\": 6366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It takes special commitment and special attention.\", \"from\": 6367, \"to\": 6417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"special commitment\", \"from\": 6376, \"to\": 6394}, {\"ngram\": \"special attention\", \"from\": 6399, \"to\": 6416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it helped that she set this goal going into the season.\", \"from\": 6418, \"to\": 6477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this goal\", \"from\": 6445, \"to\": 6454}, {\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 6466, \"to\": 6476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jade knew what she wanted.\\\"\", \"from\": 6478, \"to\": 6505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jade\", \"from\": 6478, \"to\": 6482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The simple question though, is why?\", \"from\": 6507, \"to\": 6542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The simple question\", \"from\": 6507, \"to\": 6526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carey could easily streamline her life, and no one would think less of her for it.\", \"from\": 6543, \"to\": 6625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6543, \"end\": 6548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1871048703113533e-26, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her life\", \"from\": 6573, \"to\": 6581}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 6587, \"to\": 6593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She already has given Oregon State plenty - her fourth-place finish in last year's national all-around was the program's best since 1993, and in her first two seasons she won the Pac-12 all-around title.\", \"from\": 6626, \"to\": 6829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Oregon State\", \"from\": 6648, \"to\": 6660}, {\"ngram\": \"her fourth-place finish\", \"from\": 6670, \"to\": 6693}, {\"ngram\": \"the pr